              <section>

                  
          <div data-content-element-selector="p, .js-buylink-item-container" data-allowed-classes-selector="js-buylink-item-container">
                <p dir="ltr">Two of the biggest console exclusives in the works are Marvel's Wolverine for PS5 and Perfect Dark for Xbox Series X|S. Fascinatingly enough, the creative director for the former has swapped to take over the same position at the latter game from Microsoft's The Initiative and Crystal Dynamics.</p><p dir="ltr"><a href="https://www.gamefile.news/p/wolverine-perfect-dark-brian-horton-playstation-xbox" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Game File</a> reported that Brian Horton hasn't been overseeing Wolverine since sometime this summer. In fact, Horton left Insomniac Games altogether to become creative director on <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/perfect-dark-everything-we-know/1100-6505937/" data-ref-id="1100-6505937">Perfect Dark</a>. An Xbox spokesperson told Game File that he is â€œbringing his wealth of experience to the upcoming reboot of the classic secret agent series."</p><div tabindex="0" data-id="287734808" data-promo-id="0" data-user-has-ads="1" data-video="{&quot;id&quot;:6464338,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Perfect%20Dark%20Gameplay%20Reveal%20Trailer%20%7C%20Xbox%20Games%20Showcase%202024&quot;,&quot;lengthSeconds&quot;:206,&quot;startTime&quot;:0,&quot;autoplay&quot;:false,&quot;share&quot;:{&quot;linkUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.gamespot.com\/videos\/perfect-dark-gameplay-reveal-trailer-xbox-games-showcase-2024\/2300-6464338\/&quot;,&quot;embedUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.gamespot.com\/videos\/embed\/6464338\/&quot;,&quot;embedHtml&quot;:{&quot;640&quot;:&quot;\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<iframe src=\&quot;https:\/\/www.gamespot.com\/videos\/embed\/6464338\/\&quot; height=\&quot;360\&quot; width=\&quot;640\&quot; scrolling=\&quot;no\&quot; frameborder=\&quot;\&quot; webkitAllowFullScreen mozallowfullscreen allowFullScreen><\/iframe>&quot;,&quot;480&quot;:&quot;\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<iframe src=\&quot;https:\/\/www.gamespot.com\/videos\/embed\/6464338\/\&quot; height=\&quot;270\&quot; width=\&quot;480\&qu